[2]
Date: Wed 6 Nov 2013
Source: Xinhua News Agency [in Spanish, trans., summ., edited]
http://spanish.xinhuanet.com/sociedad/2013-11/07/c_132865350.htm


Bolivia is about to be declared free of FMD and certification is planned for 2014, announced the Deputy Minister of Rural Development, Victor Hugo Vasquez, on Wednesday [6 Nov 2013].

